  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To evaluate the effectiveness of pimecrolimus cream 1% in the long-term management in mild to moderate atopic dermatitis in pediatric patients in a daily practice, as assessed by: • Investigator Global Assessment • Facial Investigator Global Ass</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
